    "description": "Delve deeper into a dangerous and mysterious cave and the remnants of miners from the future within it. As time-travelers make use of an otherwise useless radioactive crystal in Raya's town, there is a sudden explosion deep in the mines and Raya knows she must save the miners within.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBounce off of surfaces with Raya's trusty Rapier- who knows what other purposes it may serve?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nExplore each of the 6 layers of the cave, each with their own visuals, gimmicks, and gameplay elements!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDelve deeper with Grim Paths- alternate, harder levels with contrasting visuals and unique gameplay to their counterparts.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCollect Kodinium for an additional and completely optional challenge. Collecting 4 in a layer unlocks its Grim Path!",
